mg src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n5GHZ入到房係用唔到<br />\n<br />\n上面係2.4ghz既speed</blockquote><br />\n離router半米到用5ghz，睇下咩速度"},{"pid":"80dde0e3d79dd12642e9372ef36cdb999a7ef2d3","tid":184254,"uid":52216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T10:09:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你連2.4定5先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n5GHZ入到房係用唔到<br />\n<br />\n上面係2.4ghz既speed</blockquote><br />\n離router半米到用5ghz，睇下咩速度</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用iphone 7plus test 得50mbps 都唔夠"},{"pid":"e8597514befaec1be529141def0f26180da01066","tid":184254,"uid":52216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T10:09:22.000Z","msg":"係router 問題？"},{"pid":"6607b43dbeb01d9b08b35ba18da92ba8e59eedb9","tid":184254,"uid":52671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:50:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇下wifi channel有冇同人撞</blockquote><br />\n撞都唔會差咁遠"},{"pid":"4ff24e93ca846747cf4dc44c430af468b17bc13a","tid":184254,"uid":52671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:55:45.000Z","msg":"我試過剔左 wmm 就好似你咁, <br />\n你去router 設定搵下"},{"pid":"872e4e67117c849948c5f8052a729cbecc057df2","tid":184254,"uid":93620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:59:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇下wifi channel有冇同人撞</blockquote><br />\n撞都唔會差咁遠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n5G 撞channel差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一撞我間房收唔到，手動轉返channel就收返三格"},{"pid":"085ab93ec21e5d165fd0e162ad902c55dc1f0ddd","tid":184254,"uid":31307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:00:21.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n1000Mb上網 直連電話都係唔夠100Mb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2509a9372c50d00877a0ea5890ef9499a5bb9db1","tid":184254,"uid":31307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:00:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同樓主一樣嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n1000Mb上網 直連電<span style=\"color: red;\">腦</span>都係唔夠100Mb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"786003e10fa8ddf7b1c6d7416bc10588753b86c0","tid":184254,"uid":52671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T05:20:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同樓主一樣嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n1000Mb上網 直連電<span style=\"color: red;\">腦</span>都係唔夠100Mb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n你router唔係gigabit lan"},{"pid":"ed168592d54e2741a62e3ba6a67ce7570be8f63b","tid":184254,"uid":22359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T05:29:52.000Z","msg":"搭單問一問<br />\n我最近轉左用1000mb，用router淨係駁電腦就有9xxmb<br />\nIphone 6s plus用5ghz 測得1xxmb，再駁埋另一個ap router淨係用黎放大信號，電腦就變左得3-400mb左右<br />\nWifi就永遠都唔過200mb ,check過冇撞channel<br />\n係咪算正常？"},{"pid":"dd54eaa4fa95b48161ecb2377abf258dee1bcf34","tid":184254,"uid":67338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T14:08:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單問一問<br />\n我最近轉左用1000mb，用router淨係駁電腦就有9xxmb<br />\nIphone 6s plus用5ghz 測得1xxmb，再駁埋另一個ap router淨係用黎放大信號，電腦就變左得3-400mb左右<br />\nWifi就永遠都唔過200mb ,check過冇撞channel<br />\n係咪算正常？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n行緊AC ROUTER就CHECK哂有無行番80Mhz<br />\n<br />\nN機就set番40Mhz<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nchannel 自己轉下,睇下邊個最好<br />\n<br />\n以前用totolink,要行36,44先有最佳效能.行149果類就慢d<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nauto channel就盡量避免用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋要睇埋你依加用緊乜野router,wifi card.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n電話果類就算吧.好多都係1t1r.即係行AC理論上都係AC433Mhz(即係標示AC750既router理論極速)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我部電腦行USB3.0 WIFI AC 2T2R卡,標住係867Mhz mode.但係實質其實2xMB/S左右"},{"pid":"f0c679c7bf97ad59e139428ebc682dd8bb10334c","tid":184254,"uid":52216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T13:37:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/08/213740_9296f14017b22903347e